      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALDEBARANSTILINSKI (2) enjoyed the switch back from a standing start when he led and cruised home by more than 12m here last start, the second time in a row that he has scored when starting behind a mobile. Can take advantage of another good draw so looks the one to beat. AJAY VOLSTEAD (3) made it two wins from his last three starts when he scored by 4 metres last week. Both of those victories were from a standing start but he drops to a distance where his strike rate stands at 50 per cent. It's been a while between drinks for GOLDEN SUNSET (6) but she continues to race well, adding to a string of top-four finishes when second from this barrier last time out. ZEALOUS SPUR NZ (4) came from a 30m handicap to be beaten only 4m by AJAY VOLSTEAD last week and did score a win from this barrier last month.",
